    "The limitations discussed in the studies further underscore this note.",
    "These models can generate false information (termed \"hallucination\") which can be seamlessly and confidently integrated into real information (Sorin et al. 2020a, b).",
    "They can also perpetuate disparities in healthcare (Sorin et al. 2021; Kotek et al. 2023).",
    "The inherent inability to trace the exact decision-making process of these algorithms is a major challenge for trust and clinical integration (Sorin et al. 2023a, b, c).",
    "LLMs can also be vulnerable to cyber-attacks (Sorin et al. 2023a, b, c)."
